text = "Moon Navigation:
- Left click & drag with the mouse to rotate around the moon!
- Mouse scroll  or W/D keys to zoom in!
- Q/E to control vertical rotation!
- Left click on locations to move to view that location, and any available actions!

Character Panel:
- Drag dice from panel to complete actions at locations!
- End hour will reset your dice, but you must spend all of your dice beforehand!

Location Navigation:
- Dragging dice onto the various actions at a location will let you attempt to complete the task!
- Pressing 'Return to Map' in the top left corner will bring you back to the world moon view!"

